The dish was delicious and very easy to make. However, I had to cook it longer than the recipe called for, and I had to add about 1 1/2 cups of broth. I also added 1 cup of peas at the end--delicious but would have been just as good without. This recipe is much easier than many others I've seen; will definitely make again.

