Rating: 4
Note: When I visited Italy last Summer, they emphatically recommended that I not add cheese to any seafood dishes. Since that time I've followed that rule and agree wholeheartedly with their recommendations. A couple of tips - do not substitute arborio rice, make sure you stir this dish constantly ***with a wooden spoon*** and cook only very briefly after you add the reserved shrimp cooking liquid. It will be perfect!

